## Frontend Tests

### Running Tests
```bash
# From frontend/ — vitest config lives in vite.config.ts
cd frontend && npx vitest run

# Watch mode
cd frontend && npx vitest

# Type checks
cd frontend && npm run typecheck
cd frontend && npm run typecheck:test
```

### Test Structure (22 test files under `frontend/src/__tests__/`)
